{"tid":2452613,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【麻省Tufts University宣佈將關閉孔子學院】","createTime":"2021-03-19T02:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T09:55:45.000Z","uid":52779,"like":110,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"63bacf609024e79b604bf2fca0846b8ef115b134","tid":2452613,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"麻省唯一一個孔子學院將會在九月關閉，過去我和波士頓的藏、港、台、維吾爾族朋友一直要求Tufts終止與校內孔子學院的合約，除了寫信到校長Anthony Monaco及發起聯署，亦有在校園舉行示威遊行，以及與州議員講及有關問題，希望從不同途徑向學校管理層施壓。後來聯盟更發起週間遊行，每個星期到校園示威，最終校方在昨日向教職員發電郵，宣佈將不會與學院續約。<br />\n<br />\n孔子學院是中國一個跨國、跨學府的教育計劃，由隸屬中國教育部的組織Hanban（國家漢語國際推廣領導小組辦公室）資助及統籌，在全球有超過500間分校，當中有50所設於美國的學校，包括頂尖大學The George Washington University及Columbia University。<br />\n<br />\n孔子學院以宣揚中國語文及文化為名，提供洗腦教育為實，在校園教程中滲入扭曲的歷史及觀念，抹滅中國在89年天安門鎮壓、屠殺藏人、清洗維吾爾族等行為。同時他們又在校園監示學生及課程內容，經常向學校施壓把敏感資訊及惹爭議的人士剔除。<br />\n<br />\n2018年，Tufts一位校園活動講者的簡介在學院總監的要求下，被刪減有關台灣的內容。後來Tufts一度因反對聲音而停止學院運作一年，當時學校為此設立的委員會曾指出Tufts自2015年開始，總共收到中國$409,810去營運該校的孔子學院。<br />\n同年美國國會通過Defense Authorization Act，阻止有設立孔子學院的大學獲得資助用於語言教學，令至少27所大學關閉孔子學院，包括麻省大學的波士頓分校。2019年參議院報告顯示中國政府在13年間提供超過一億美金，在超過100間美國學校設立及運作孔子學院，包括幼兒園及中小學。<br />\n<br />\nTufts的孔子學院將於九月合約完滿，終止運作。校方表示他們樂意循不同途徑讓學生可以有交流活動，接觸中國語文及文化。現時Tufts依然有到北京的出國交流計劃，保持與北京師範大學的密切來往。<br />\n<br />\nShout out to Students for a Free Tibet Boston Uyghur Association 波士頓香港人權組織 Hong Kong Social Action Movements in Boston Formosan Association for Public Affairs Tibetan Association of Boston<br />\n&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;<br />\n許穎婷 Frances Hui<br />\n⧐ Instagram: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/hui_wingting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhui_wingting&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBStjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=6c794481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/hui_wingting</a><br />\n⧐ Twitter: <a href=\"http://twitter.com/frances_hui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffrances_hui&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBStjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=0f41d2ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/frances_hui</a><br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2317436205144840/posts/2846792235542565/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2317436205144840%2Fposts%2F2846792235542565%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBStjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=2f73522e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2317436205144840/posts/2846792235542565/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/3/17/n12818413.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F3%2F17%2Fn12818413.htm&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBStjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=9b1fb6f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/3/17/n12818413.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/kejiaowen/cm-03182021105521.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fkejiaowen%2Fcm-03182021105521.html&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBStjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=21861cdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/kejiaowen/cm-03182021105521.html</a>"},{"pid":"ace5493151b81f34f82d000685e26ce70581d9d0","tid":2452613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c83c5ea4d4253ef2387e9363b2f72540b55d250","tid":2452613,"uid":335924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/c